data.description: This NorthStar built home with 4bd/2.5ba is located in the highly sought after Berkley Hills subdivision. This home features three car attached garage, covered front and back porches. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, kitchen island and stained cabinetry.  The spacious owner's suite features cathedral ceiling, large closet, dual vanities, separate shower and garden tub.  There is also a $5,000 allowance (Paint, Closing Costs, Etc.)  VA Assumable loan at 3.75% to qualified buyers.
